<plot>In Pacaembu, one of the most aristocratic neighborhoods in São Paulo, an empty house is used as a shelter for a homeless mother and her daughter. As time goes by, two other people having the same social status come to live there too, establishing a conflict. They're not beggars, but icons of an impoverished Brazilian middle class.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?278161</url></doc>
